5. KEY INSIGHTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Top 5 Features Most Correlated with Mental Health Risk (positive):
  productivity_score            :   0.355
  mental_health_history         :   0.014
  employment_status             :   0.011
  social_support_score          :   0.010
  sleep_hours                   :   0.005

Top 5 Features Most Correlated with Mental Health Risk (negative):
  age                           :  -0.009
  physical_activity_days        :  -0.022
  seeks_treatment               :  -0.032
  anxiety_score                 :  -0.246
  depression_score              :  -0.370

Strongest Correlations Between Features (excluding target):
  depression_score          <-> productivity_score            :  -0.939
  depression_score          <-> mental_health_risk            :  -0.370
  productivity_score        <-> mental_health_risk            :   0.355
  anxiety_score             <-> mental_health_risk            :  -0.246
  seeks_treatment           <-> mental_health_risk            :  -0.032
  age                       <-> anxiety_score                 :   0.025
  physical_activity_days    <-> mental_health_risk            :  -0.022
  stress_level              <-> social_support_score          :   0.020
  sleep_hours               <-> employment_status             :   0.019
  anxiety_score             <-> social_support_score          :  -0.018

